        <p>I am a passionate problem solver who enjoys using technology to create meaningful solutions. My expertise includes data analysis, programming, and visualization. I love working with Python, SQL, and tools that help bring insights to life. My projects range from building interactive applications to analyzing large datasets, always with a focus on efficiency and innovation.</p>
